{"tid":953737,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西安高校老鼠橫行 20歲學生染病亡 宿舍床鋪滿佈屎尿","createTime":"2018-12-24T07:04:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-24T07:17:35.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d18efc1c0ceab7a8c0a814ef660006fbdf2332ef","tid":953737,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T07:04:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181221/_2018122121255960805.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181221%2F_2018122121255960805.jpg&h=9765b879&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n西安醫學高等專科學校一名男學生感染出血熱（漢坦病毒），經過3天搶救無效，於本月17日死亡。家長認為，兒子患病和宿舍鼠患肆虐有直接關係。西安醫學高等專科學校辦公室昨日表示，學校只發現了一宗出血熱病例，學校最近一直在處理此事，並進行消毒工作。<br />\n<br />\n死者家長透露，兒子今年20歲，2017年考入西安醫學高等專科學校。本月月12日，兒子在校期間出現發熱、意識不清等症狀，14日在同學陪同下前往醫院就診，檢查後初步診斷流行性出血熱，並將血樣本送至進一步檢查，確診為出血熱。<br />\n<br />\n兒子轉院至感染性疾病科加護病房，經過3天搶救，17日醫院告知多器官衰竭、腦幹死亡，家屬決定宣布放棄治療。<br />\n<br />\n家長透露，兒子回家多次反映宿舍有老鼠出沒，曾親眼看到學生床鋪到處是老鼠屎尿。在尋找有可能出入老鼠的通道發現，宿舍隔壁垃圾桶打開、垃圾遍地，老鼠、蚊蠅四出。<br />\n<br />\n該校學生反映。從今年開學起，宿舍就有許多老鼠屎，並抓住過一兩窩老鼠，還用粘鼠板粘住過4隻老鼠，曾多次向輔導員和宿管人員反映。<br />\n<br />\n學校事後開始做消毒工作。宿舍其他人本月14日晚搬離，2天後死者生前隔壁宿舍又發現了許多老鼠，該宿舍學生也已調換。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181221/_2018122121260090508.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181221%2F_2018122121260090508.jpg&h=9941b795&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181221/_2018122121260120536.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181221%2F_2018122121260120536.jpg&h=1942e4e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/894085\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F894085&d=s%2BPAoeUTXyRCnWzRG5Mam3adZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=017abde8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F894085&h=27c9ca62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/894085</a>"},{"pid":"5aea46ec326d1a57fb6dc52a193d9713d2457f48","tid":953737,"uid":80924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T07:06:47.000Z","msg":"嘩屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f276bacff0e46326eac53ca8c4bf32f1f5c18ba6","tid":953737,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T07:07:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e31d16663183bfdd90f5d1929efa3e9754ba9efe","tid":953737,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T07:07:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f94ad4ae385c6a5898dc938af243c929fdb0cfb0","tid":953737,"uid":200495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T07:10:54.000Z","msg":"讀醫都冇啲常識（學校甚至學生）<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d633e429d06573f1110a809bde19f1525a92b7f9","tid":953737,"uid":171058,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T07:14:59.000Z","msg":"醫學院都咁L樣<br />\n大陸真係冇L得救"},{"pid":"33c532c8a6763e679ca824177922c331681d0c3d","tid":953737,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d633e429d06573f1110a809bde19f1525a92b7f9","tid":953737,"uid":171058,"l